Definition at line 131 of file CopyrightHolder.h.

map_t CopyrightHolder::m_boxesByParent [private]
 

Table describing the parent / child relationship for the CopyrightNotices.

pair_t::first is the parent id, and pair_t::second refers to the child id. The id:s are the position in the m_boxes vector.

Parent id MAX_INT32 means that there is no parent, i.e. the box is at the top / root level.
